Description: Check Point SNX VPN plugin for NetworkManager
 This package provides NetworkManager integration for Check Point SNX VPN.
 It allows connecting to Check Point VPN servers directly from
 GNOME Settings, COSMIC Settings, or any NetworkManager-compatible
 network configuration tool.
 .
 Features:
  - Full NetworkManager integration
  - Support for multiple simultaneous VPN connections
  - IPSec and SSL VPN tunnel support
  - Multi-factor authentication (MFA/OTP) support
